asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2007-2011 Toyota Tundra and 2008-2011 Toyota Sequoia with the 5.7L V8 engine.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=77-9031-1KP

K&N 77-9031-1KP metal air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 13.4 horsepower at 5142 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer.
